query:
INSERT INTO data.entities_place (
            canonical_name,
            category,
            geo_center,
            cluster_radius_meters,
            metadata
        ) VALUES (
            $1,
            $2,
            ST_SetSRID(ST_MakePoint($3, $4), 4326)::geography,
            50.0,
            $5
        )
        RETURNING id, canonical_name
